he is alive ✝️

my birthday has never fallen on Easter before, so my heart is feeling dandelion soft today:) i can only pray that any memory of the years i live will testify of the living Son of God. i am sure his heavenly throne is every kind of majesty my human heart could never imagine, but i know he leaves that throne and majesty to find us in the darkest corners, the unknowable depths. he walks this earth to seek our hearts until we are found. what a love. 

thank you for the birthday wishes today!!! happiest Easter, my angel friends!
